narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend MCDB 415 for students who have taken a physiology course previously and is looking for an easier upper level MCDB course for the major.

One of the more low workload MCDB classes. Lectures are hard to go to in the morning and when notes/lectures are posted online but lectures are definitely helpful if you can keep focused. There's quite a bit of material covered for both the midterm and final, and know that it wasn't take home for this semester, but rather in class.
